sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ROLE-PRIMARY-USER
    participant UI as SCREEN-PRIMARY
    participant API as API-CREATE
    participant Reviewer as ROLE-REVIEWER
    participant System as ROLE-SYSTEM

    User->>UI: submit primary request
    UI->>API: validate and create
    API-->>Reviewer: pending review available
    Reviewer->>API: approve or reject
    API-->>System: emit side effects when approved
    System-->>User: final status visible
